<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="nerve-n">nerve <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /nɜːv/    美 /nɜːrv/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>神经：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>nerve cells / endings
神经细胞/末梢</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[用复数] 神经紧张；焦躁：</strong></h4>
<h4 id="3u">3.<strong>[U] 勇气；意志力</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="get-on-sbs-nerves">get on sb’s nerves</h3>
<p>1.<strong>令某人焦躁：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Stop whistling! It’s getting on my nerves!
别吹口哨了!扰得我心烦!</p></div></div>